4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that aims to teach students to become data scientists and build their first ML models. The course is designed for beginners and requires no previous knowledge. The program is 16 weeks long and consists of 3 classes per week. The class size is limited to 12 people. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python and libraries like Pandas and Numpy. They will also explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also focuses on real-life case studies and industry-standard tools. Students will have the opportunity to strategize and develop their own AI projects. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit the [website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop